001package edu.cnm.deepdive.zoomattendance.model.entity;
002
003import androidx.annotation.NonNull;
004import androidx.room.ColumnInfo;
005import androidx.room.Entity;
006import androidx.room.ForeignKey;
007import androidx.room.Index;
008import androidx.room.PrimaryKey;
009import java.time.Instant;
010
011@Entity(
012    tableName = "zoom_meeting",
013    foreignKeys = {
014        @ForeignKey(
015            entity = Student.class,
016            parentColumns = "student_id", childColumns = "student_id", onDelete = ForeignKey.SET_NULL
017        )
018    },
019    indices = {
020        @Index(value = {"uuid", "student_id"}, unique = true),
021        @Index(value = {"uuid", "created"}, unique = true)
022    }
023)
024public class ZoomMeeting {
025
026  @PrimaryKey(autoGenerate = true)
027  @ColumnInfo(name = "zoom_meeting_id")
028  private long id;
029
030  @ColumnInfo(index = true)
031  private String uuid;
032
033  @ColumnInfo(name = "student_id", index = true)
034  private Long studentId;
035
036  @NonNull
037  private Instant created = Instant.MIN;
038
039  @NonNull
040  private Instant started = Instant.MIN;
041
042  private long duration;
043
044  private String topic;
045
046  public Long getStudentId() {
047    return studentId;
048  }
049
050  public void setStudentId(Long studentId) {
051    this.studentId = studentId;
052  }
053
054  public String getUuid() {
055    return uuid;
056  }
057
058  public void setUuid(String uuid) {
059    this.uuid = uuid;
060  }
061
062  public long getId() {
063    return id;
064  }
065
066  public void setId(long id) {
067    this.id = id;
068  }
069
070  @NonNull
071  public Instant getCreated() {
072    return created;
073  }
074
075  public void setCreated(@NonNull Instant created) {
076    this.created = created;
077  }
078
079  @NonNull
080  public Instant getStarted() {
081    return started;
082  }
083
084  public void setStarted(@NonNull Instant started) {
085    this.started = started;
086  }
087
088  public long getDuration() {
089    return duration;
090  }
091
092  public void setDuration(long duration) {
093    this.duration = duration;
094  }
095
096  public String getTopic() {
097    return topic;
098  }
099
100  public void setTopic(String topic) {
101    this.topic = topic;
102  }
103}
